Call CHARGE_DEFITMDES("DES1AXX",GLANGUE,[F:ITM]ITMREF,[M:LPNA]ITMDES1(nolign-1), "[F:ITM]") From TRTX3 # FGR 03/07/2009 : X3SUIVI56319
Read [LPN]LPN0 = [M:LPNA]LPNNUMDES(nolign-1)
[M:LPNA]TCTRNUM(nolign-1) = [F:LPN]TCTRNUM
Return

