  Actzo [M:LPNA]ECSSEL
Endif

Chgfmt [M:LPNA]MODAFFLPN  With "LA2789"
[M:LPNA]MODAFFLPN = 2
Grizo [M:LPNA]25
Actzo [M:LPNA]MODAFFLPN
